NK041(di)030:1: // sgeg rdor lugs kyi bla bslu bcu gsum ma'i chog
NK041(di)030:2: bsgrigs bklags pas kun shes go gsal du bkod pa
NK041(di)030:3: srog gi btsan rdzong zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK041(di)030:4: dbang gi rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)030:5: byin rlabs gzi brjid nyi ma 'bum 'od 'phro //
NK041(di)030:6: dngos grub nor bu'i char rgyun gang 'dod bsnyil //
NK041(di)030:7: glog ltar myur ba'i phrin las yid bzhin sgrub //
NK041(di)030:8: rtsa gsum lha la 'dud do dgyes brtses skyongs //
NK041(di)030:9: lus rten chags dang gnas pa'i gzhi //
NK041(di)030:10: bla tshe nyams pa gso ba'i thabs //
NK041(di)030:11: grub pa'i zhal lung gzi byin can //
NK041(di)030:12: 'khrul med lag tu blang bder dgod //
NK041(di)030:13: grub pa'i slob dpon chen po sgeg pa rdo rjes
NK041(di)030:14: bkral ba'i bla bslu bcu gsum mar grags pa 'di
NK041(di)030:18: gsum pa rtags la dpyad pa'o //
NK041(di)030:19: dang po dgra yul du bla 'khyams pa bla dur
NK041(di)030:20: du zhugs pa bla gshin pos khyer ba sogs kyi
NK041(di)030:21: ltas su rang ngam gzhan sgren mo'am gcer bu bud
NK041(di)030:22: pa rmis na nges par bla khyer ba yin cing
NK041(di)030:23: / gzhan yang 'byung ba dgra thog tu song ba sogs skeg la babs pa /
NK041(di)030:24: dngos su sems rnal du mi pheb pa'i yed yed
NK041(di)030:25: pa dang mtshan mo rtag tu gnyid skrag sad byed
NK041(di)030:26: pa sogs bla 'khyams pa'i rtags yin pas phyi bshol
NK041(di)030:27: le lo'i dbang du ma song bar 'phral du bla
NK041(di)030:28: tshe bslu ba'i thabs la 'bad dgos so //
NK041(di)030:29: gnyis pa bcos thabs la gsum /
NK041(di)030:30: sbyor ba bcas gshom bya ba /
NK041(di)030:31: dngos gzhi cho ga'i rim pa /
NK041(di)030:32: rjes mjug chog gi las rim mo //
NK041(di)030:34: phug logs su yi dam gang la byed pa'i gtor mchod rang gzhung ltar bsham /
NK041(di)030:35: tshe sgrub dang sbrel na dkyil 'khor tshe rdzas sogs
NK041(di)030:36: rgyas par bkod pa'i mdun nam logs gang bder stegs
NK041(di)030:37: bu'am sle'u'i khar rdul tshon gyis mi gzugs skye mched
NK041(di)030:38: dod cing gcer bu rkang lag brkyangs te gan rkyal
NK041(di)030:40: de mthar mu khyud gnyis zlum por bskor ba'i bar phyogs mtshams brgyad du phye ba'i shar shing /
NK041(di)030:44: mtshams bzhi sa'i gnas te spar kha'i gnas yul yin
NK041(di)030:45: pas gtsug lag dang mthun par shing sogs la rim
NK041(di)030:46: bzhin ljang dmar dkar mthing ser po'i mdog tu bya
NK041(di)030:47: / de'i mthar re kh+aa gru bzhir bcad pa phyogs mtshams brgyad du phye ba'i shar dkar /
NK041(di)030:51: mtshams bzhi kun khyab kyi dbang du byas pa'i mdzes tshon gang bder bya /
NK041(di)030:52: rgyun du rdul tshon mi lcog na ras sam shog
NK041(di)030:53: bu la chu tshon gyis gong gsal dape'u ris ltar
NK041(di)030:54: bris pa'i ming gzugs kyi snying gar bsgrub bya pho
NK041(di)030:55: mo gang yin gyi 'dra glud mtho gang sor bzhi
NK041(di)030:56: las mi chung ba ngar phye riin chen sman sna
NK041(di)030:57: bsres pas bzos pa skye mched dod cing tshon rtsis
NK041(di)030:58: kha bsgyur bar gyon 'phro'i gos bgo ba dang bcas
NK041(di)030:59: dar sogs glud gos bzang pos g.yogs pa'i mdun du
NK041(di)030:76: zas sman gos dar snam bu 'bru dang bcas pa so sor sne 'dus tshang ba dang /
NK041(di)030:80: g.yon du byang rdzas lan tsh+wa /
NK041(di)030:81: bul tog sogs yul de dang de nas thon pa'i rigs /
NK041(di)030:82: mdun rgyab tu la rdzas tsh+wa la /
NK041(di)030:84: klud rdzas bye ma sgog gtsong zam shing sogs dang
NK041(di)030:85: bcas pa rin po che'i snod du bkod pa'i lag
NK041(di)030:86: g.yas su gser / g.yon du g.yu /
NK041(di)030:87: rgyab tu nam mkha' khong pa khams mthun 'ja' ris can /
NK041(di)030:91: pho yin na phrag pa g.yas su stag pa dang /
NK041(di)030:92: mo yin na g.yon du glang ma'i byang bu lo grangs kyi khram ris bris pa bcas gzugs /
NK041(di)030:93: glud spyi 'gror lus ngag yid gsum mtshon pa'i mar me gsum mdun du bzhag pa'i srol yang snang /
NK041(di)030:94: ched du dmigs nas bsad pa ma yin pa'i lug
NK041(di)030:95: gi bsad sha gsar pa dri nag med pa gtsang
NK041(di)030:96: ma / pho'i bla bslu na lug gi rkang pa g.yas kyi sha dang /
NK041(di)030:97: mo'i bla bslu na lug gi rkang pa g.yon gyi sha dgos pa khyad par ba /
NK041(di)030:98: pho mo gang yin kyang sha de'i khud du bla
NK041(di)030:99: g.yu dang lo grangs ci lon gyi grangs dang bstun
NK041(di)030:100: pa'i nas dkar rdog bcas dar dkar dri med kyis
NK041(di)030:101: bstums nas bcug pa'i sha de'i phyi bal dang ras
NK041(di)030:102: dkar dri med kyis dril ba yon bdag gi the'usa
NK041(di)030:103: mnan la pho yin na ngar glud kyi g.yas dang
NK041(di)030:104: mo yin na ngar glud kyi g.yon du 'jog /
NK041(di)030:105: shin tu do gal can la rgya shog la byin
NK041(di)030:106: rten bsres pa'i mtshal gyis tshe bsnyen lta bu'i yi
NK041(di)030:107: dam gyi snying po dang bla 'gugs sngags byang gsham
NK041(di)030:108: du 'gugs pa'i 'dod gsol bris pa'i shog byang gis
NK041(di)030:109: bla rten dkris pa'i rgyab tu bal sogs kyis bstum
NK041(di)030:110: pa dang / bla lug la'ang nang gzhug de ltar byed pa zhal shes su snang /
NK041(di)030:111: de'i mthar mi gzugs kyi lus kyi lhu bcu gnyis te /
NK041(di)030:117: stod smad gnyis te bcu gnyis dang /
NK041(di)030:118: mgo dang bcu gsum kyi khar sa'am zan la bcos pa'i nas phul re dang /
NK041(di)030:119: yon bdag gi 'dra glud ngar zan la bzos pa
NK041(di)030:120: mdzub gang ba re'i rgyab tu nam mkha' 'ja' ma
NK041(di)030:124: pho mo dang sbyar ba'i stag pa glang ma gang bde'i byang bu so so'i gdong can rnams gzug /
NK041(di)030:128: rje ngar gyi sha du ma re /
NK041(di)030:129: zhal bur chang phud blug pa re re ste tshan bcu gsum tshang nges pa bzhag /
NK041(di)030:130: mi gzugs rkang lag sogs kyi bar dang mu khyud
NK041(di)030:131: kyi nang bcas par pho mo gang yin gyi bla
NK041(di)030:132: rtags so so'i mtshan ma dang ldan pa'i /
NK041(di)030:140: ra lug rnams kyi gzugs zan las skye mched dod
NK041(di)030:141: cing rang mdog gis bsgyur ba kha nang du bstan
NK041(di)030:142: la bzhag / de'i mthar mu khyud spar kha'i gnas
NK041(di)030:143: yul brgyad la 'jim stegs su spar kha'i rang mdog
NK041(di)030:144: gi khong pa bsgyur cing mtha' 'ja' ris can gyi
NK041(di)030:145: la bzhag / nam mkha' / rgyang bu 'phan bzang gis spras pa /
NK041(di)030:150: mdun du yon bdag gi 'dra glud /
NK041(di)030:153: mtheb kyu dang bcas pa tshar brgyad bkod pa'i thog /
NK041(di)030:154: spar kha so so'i gdon gyi sde brgyad sdong zla
NK041(di)030:155: dang bcas pa'i gzugs brnyan tsakli dang shing byang gang
NK041(di)030:157: lhor btsan mi dmar rta dmar go khrab can dang
NK041(di)030:158: gri bo mi dmar nag khro nyams ral pa gzengs
NK041(di)030:159: pa / lho nub tu sa bdag ser po rgyal
NK041(di)030:160: po'i chas la thod can dang phu bdag mi dkar
NK041(di)030:162: nub tu bdud mi nag rta nag ber nag gyon pa dang skyes bu dkar po gos dkar can /
NK041(di)030:163: nub byang du rgyal 'gong ser skya btsun gzugs zhwa
NK041(di)030:164: ser can dang the'u rang byis pa dkar skya gtsug
NK041(di)030:165: phud can / byang du klu sngon po sbrul mjug
NK041(di)030:166: dang sbrul gdengs can dang ma mo bud med nag
NK041(di)030:167: mo dar nag gi go zu can drel nag zhon
NK041(di)030:168: phud can / pa / byang shar du rbad 'dre
NK041(di)030:169: dang dkor 'dre gnyis ka mi gzugs gos nag dang
NK041(di)030:170: gos ser gyon nas lag pa gdengs pa /
NK041(di)030:171: shar du rgyal po bswe thebs dang gzan sham can
NK041(di)030:172: dkar po glang la zhon pa dang klu sman gong
NK041(di)030:173: mtshungs / shar lhor rgyal 'gong gong mtshungs dang smyo 'dre nag po gcer bu ral pa gzengs pa /
NK041(di)030:174: thams cad kyang gzugs skye mched dod cing lag gnyis
NK041(di)030:175: gdengs te glud la rngams pa'i tshul can bcas bkod
NK041(di)030:176: / de mthar phyogs mtshams brgyad dang steng 'og mtshon
NK041(di)030:177: byed shar nub bcas par 'jim stegs thog nam rgyang
NK041(di)030:178: mda' 'phang shing byang la srid pa spyi ris bris
NK041(di)030:179: pa rnams tshar bcu bkod pa'i thog /
NK041(di)030:180: phyogs kyi gdon chen bcu'i gzugs dgos pas lding khri
NK041(di)030:181: lta bu yod na steng 'og sogs ci lta bar
NK041(di)030:182: kod pa de yang de bzhin ma thub na phyogs
NK041(di)030:186: de'ang tsakli shing byang gang bade'am /
NK041(di)030:187: 'jim gzugs byed pa gang rigs kyis gdon chen gyi
NK041(di)030:188: gzugs khro tshul rngams pa dar chen gyi ber dang
NK041(di)030:189: thod / g.yas dar mdung phyar zhir g.yon zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK041(di)030:190: rta mchog sga srab kyis spras par 'gying tshul gyis
NK041(di)030:191: zhon pa'i steng du bya lding zhing rol du khyi
NK041(di)030:193: ber thod dar mdung zhags pa rta bya khyi bcas
NK041(di)030:194: so so'i rang mdog dang mtshungs par dgos pa ste
NK041(di)030:196: shar du rgyal po dang dri za'i gdon dkar po /
NK041(di)030:197: lhor gshin rje dang grul bum gdon ser po /
NK041(di)030:198: nub tu klu'i gdon dmar po /
NK041(di)030:199: byang du gnod sbyin gdon ljang gu /
NK041(di)030:200: mtshams kyi shar lhor me lha /
NK041(di)030:203: byang shar du dbang ldan rnams khra bo /
NK041(di)030:204: 'og gi sa bdag nag po'i gdon dud kha bya'o //
NK041(di)030:205: 'di rnams tsakli byed na spar kha'i gdon gnyis re gcig tu bsdus pa'i tsakli brgyad /
NK041(di)030:206: phyogs bcu'i gdon bcu so so bcas bco brgyad dgos so //
NK041(di)030:207: gdon gzugs thams cad mgron thabs yin pas mdun phyogs la kha bstan /
NK041(di)030:208: de'i mtha' mdos dkris kyis dkri /
NK041(di)030:209: de'i g.yas g.yon gang bder yon bdag dngos yod na des khyab cing /
NK041(di)030:210: med na ras dri med kyi khar bla rten gyi gos bzang po dri ma can 'jog par bshad /
NK041(di)030:211: de'ang lag len du skyes pa g.yas dang bud med g.yon phyogs su 'jog pa dang /
NK041(di)030:212: bla dpon lta bu che gnyan gyi rigs la khri
NK041(di)030:213: rgyab yol tshul bzhin byas pa'i khar na bza' dbu
NK041(di)030:214: zhwa phyag phreng sogs bzhag par snang /
NK041(di)030:215: de'i mdun du khug rtags brtags pa'i ka to ra
NK041(di)030:216: lta bu'i snod bzang po chag rdol sogs kyi skyon
NK041(di)030:217: med pa'i nang du rgyun 'babs kyi chu sna mang
NK041(di)030:218: pos bkang ba'i steng khams mthun gyi rtsi dang ldan
NK041(di)030:220: mar ram zan bzang po la byin rten dang dri
NK041(di)030:221: bzang bsres pa'i bla lug pho mo'i rtags mtshan go
NK041(di)030:222: ma ldog par skye mched dod cing tshon rtsis spras
NK041(di)030:224: gzhan yang sde brgyad spyi'i gtor ma dang rngon cha gser skyems sogs legs par bsham mo //
NK041(di)030:225: gser skyems ni tshar re bzhin mchod dgos pas 'dzom na phud phor bcu gsum /
NK041(di)030:226: ma 'dzom na gcig gi nang du 'bru sna dang
NK041(di)030:227: rin chen phye ma btab cing chang phud blugs pa
NK041(di)030:228: mdos mdun bkod / yas rnams ma gtsang na rang
NK041(di)030:229: gi bla tshab tu khyer dogs yod par bshad pas
NK041(di)030:231: thag nor na sde brgyad 'khrugs par 'gyur pas spar
NK041(di)030:232: kha sogs kyi nam mkha'i khong pa so so'i rang
NK041(di)030:233: mdog dang 'phrod grogs kyi kha dog can ma nor
NK041(di)030:234: ba dang mthar 'ja' ris 'byung 'phrod ltar dkri /
NK041(di)030:235: glud nam gyi khong pa yon bdag gi srog khams kyi kha dog la 'phrod /
NK041(di)030:236: nang nas dgra ded dang phyi nas grogs ded 'ong ba'i rim pa lnga /
NK041(di)030:237: de rgyab 'ja' ris gong mtshungs byed pa'i phyag len snang /
NK041(di)030:238: 'grub na bla bslu 'khor lo gsung rgyun ma bris la bla rten dang mnyam du bzhag go //
NK041(di)030:239: yang bcas gshom 'bring po byed na gong smos mdos yas rnams tshang bar bkod /
NK041(di)030:240: gdon rnams dmigs pas gsal btab pa tsam las gzugs bris 'bur mi dgos /
NK041(di)030:241: bsdus pa mdos yas rnams kyang tshar bcu gsum pa la bsdu /
NK041(di)030:242: spar kha dang phyogs bcu'i gdon la zur du mi bsham par bshad mod /
NK041(di)030:243: bsgrub bya do gal dang 'byor pa la bstun par 'os so //
NK041(di)030:244: gnyis pa cho ga'i rim pa la gzhung bsrang zhing byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK041(di)030:245: bla bslu dngos la 'jug pa gnyis las /
NK041(di)030:247: dbang chen lta bu rang nyid yi dam zhi khro gang byed kyi phrin las gzhung bsrang /
NK041(di)030:248: 'dzab bsnyen chos srung skong gso tshogs dang bcas pa
NK041(di)030:249: rgyas par song ba'i mtshams su mdos byin brlab la
NK041(di)030:251: da lta phal mo ches tshe sgrub bla bslu sbrel ma byed pa grags che zhing /
NK041(di)030:252: de'i lag len kyang tshe'i phrin las lan gsum btang
NK041(di)030:253: ba'i bsnyen bzlas kyi mtshams su mdos la 'jug cing
NK041(di)030:254: bla bslu'i bzlas pa dang 'gug gzhug grub nas tshe
NK041(di)030:255: 'gugs byed / chos srung dang tshogs skor dgong mor
NK041(di)030:256: btang ba'i phyag srol 'dug pa nyid byin rlabs dge
NK041(di)030:257: 'phrod che ba nyams myong rgyun ldan du snang yang
NK041(di)030:258: 'gugs byed / / mi lcogs na snga dro tshe'i
NK041(di)030:259: phrin las rgyas par btang zhing bsnyen pa ci 'grub
NK041(di)030:260: tshe 'gug skong gso tshogs mchod lhag ma'i bar 'grub
NK041(di)030:261: 'gugs byed / / par bya / phyi dro mdos
NK041(di)030:262: btang zhing sngags bzla ba'i tshar grangs gang 'gro bya
NK041(di)030:263: ba nyid 'don bya zor yang zhing bzlas pa'i grangs
NK041(di)030:265: de'ang smad phyogs su bla bslu brgya rtsa dang stong
NK041(di)030:266: rtsa la sogs pa'i tha snyad byed cing gzhung tshar
NK041(di)030:267: grangs gyer ba gtsor bton par snang yang nus pa
NK041(di)030:268: 'byin byed dmigs bzlas kho na yin pas de nyid
NK041(di)030:270: kha cig gis rgyab dpung du sde brgyad cha snyoms
NK041(di)030:271: btang ba'i srol 'dug pa ltar btang na skabs 'dir
NK041(di)030:273: byin rlabs spyi mthun byas la tshar gcig gam gsum
NK041(di)030:274: tsam 'bul te sdong grogs byed pa'i phrin las bcol
NK041(di)030:275: / gang ltar mdos byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK041(di)030:276: yas rnams la chab bran te /
NK041(di)030:277: bdag nyid bcom ldan sh+aakya thub //
NK041(di)030:278: phyag rgya'i yi ge a dkar las //
NK041(di)030:280: dri ma sbyangs nas stong par gyur /
NK041(di)030:281: thal mo khong stong sbyar la /
NK041(di)030:282: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+hahsarba d+harmahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK041(di)030:283: lan gsum re re bzhin phyag rgya bkrol nas se gol gtogs pa phyi ma rnams la'ang 'gre /
NK041(di)030:284: chos nyid rnam dag phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)030:285: ting 'dzin bden pas gtor rdzas kyi //
NK041(di)030:286: 'bag btsog nyams grib nyes skyon dang //
NK041(di)030:287: mtshan 'dzin dri ma dag gyur cig /
NK041(di)030:288: rin chen snod du kham yig las //
NK041(di)030:289: rten 'brel rdzas las grub pa'i mi //
NK041(di)030:290: rkyen ngan zlog pa'i dpa' ngar can //
NK041(di)030:291: khog stod gser la khog smad g.yu //
NK041(di)030:292: sked pa mchong la rkang lag kun //
NK041(di)030:293: gser dngul zangs dang lcags las grub //
NK041(di)030:294: zho sha'i snying la mu tig klad //
NK041(di)030:295: lung tang mig la zer sgro'i skra //
NK041(di)030:296: byi ru'i ljags la mgron bu'i so //
NK041(di)030:297: khams dang skye mched yongs su rdzogs //
NK041(di)030:298: mda' bkra skyes pa stag chas rdzogs //
NK041(di)030:299: 'phang bkra mo btsun gser g.yus brgyan //
NK041(di)030:300: gcig las brgya stong bye ba 'phro //
NK041(di)030:302: nam mkha' bdud rtsi skyems phud dang //
NK041(di)030:303: gtor ma chang bu ting lo dang //
NK041(di)030:304: sha dum 'bru sna yas stags rnams //
NK041(di)030:305: so sor ci 'dod longs spyod rdzas //
NK041(di)030:306: sbyin bdag tshe glud srog gi skyin //
NK041(di)030:307: bu lon lan chags 'jal ba'i rdzas //
NK041(di)030:308: zag med nam mkha'i mdzod du gyur //
NK041(di)030:309: bdag nyid bcom ldan rnam snang mdzad //
NK041(di)030:310: phyag rgya'i yi ge kham sngon las //
NK041(di)030:312: nam mkha'i khams kun khyab par gyur //
NK041(di)030:313: thal mo sbub stong du sbyar ba'i tshigs bar pa
NK041(di)030:314: rnams bcag pa rin chen sgrom bu'i phyag rgya smin
NK041(di)030:316: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK041(di)030:317: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK041(di)030:318: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)030:319: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)030:320: ting 'dzin ldan pas gtor rdzas rnams //
NK041(di)030:321: bskal pa'i bar du zad mi shes //
NK041(di)030:322: rgya che nam mkha' gang gyur cig /
NK041(di)030:323: bdag nyid bcom ldan bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK041(di)030:324: phyag rgya'i yi ge h+r+aihdamara las //
NK041(di)030:326: bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin gyur //
NK041(di)030:328: sor mo gzhan rnams gshog pa ltar gdengs pa kha'i thad du bzhag la /
NK041(di)030:329: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK041(di)030:330: bdud rtsi thabs sbyor phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)030:331: ting 'dzin bden pas gtor rdzas rnams //
NK041(di)030:332: bdud rtsi ye shes lnga yi dngos //
NK041(di)030:333: 'chi gsos dug lnga'i sman gyur cig /
NK041(di)030:334: bdag nyid bcom ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK041(di)030:335: phyag rgya'i yi ge t+r+aa ser las //
NK041(di)030:337: so so'i mos pa ji bzhin gyur //
NK041(di)030:338: lag pa gnyis mdzub mo bsgreng ba'i khu tshur g.yon
NK041(di)030:339: snying gar bzhag g.yas brkyangs te rdzas la gtod pa'i
NK041(di)030:340: tshul byas la / na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK041(di)030:341: a ba lo ki te sam+b+ha ra sam+b+ha ra h+aum
NK041(di)030:342: tshul byas la / / rgya chen shugs ldan phyag rgya sngags //
NK041(di)030:343: ting 'dzin bden pas gtor rdzas rnams //
NK041(di)030:344: dbang po'i spyod yul tshim byed pa'i //
NK041(di)030:346: bdag nyid bcom ldan don yod grub //

NK041(di)030:672: rngon cha dar zab gser dang dngul //
NK041(di)030:673: lho byang la klung rdzas du ma //
NK041(di)030:674: gtor ma gser skyems bcas pa bzhes //
NK041(di)030:675: rgyu sbyor mi bu rin chen 'di'i //
NK041(di)030:676: bla la brkus sam gzhom srid na //
NK041(di)030:677: gzung ba thong la bcings pa khrol //
NK041(di)030:678: bsdams pa klod la mnan pa theg /
NK041(di)030:679: gnod pa sdus la bla tshe gtod //
NK041(di)030:680: zhi ba chen po'i ngang la bzhugs //
NK041(di)030:681: mnyam pa chen po'i ngang la bzhugs //
NK041(di)030:682: phan pa byang sems bskyed du gsol //
NK041(di)030:683: ces bsngosa pas so so nas yas stags rnams bdag gir byas /
NK041(di)030:684: mgu zhing tshims te ji ltar bsgos pa'i don bde blag tu sgrub par mos /
NK041(di)030:685: drug pa bla 'gugs kyi sngags zla ba ni /
NK041(di)030:686: rang yi dam du gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h'u las
NK041(di)030:687: 'od zer lcags kyu'i rnam pa dpag tu med pa
NK041(di)030:688: 'phros / bla ma yi dam sangs rgyas byang sems
NK041(di)030:689: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma dang bcas
NK041(di)030:690: pa'i thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK041(di)030:691: slar yang 'od zer sna tshogs steng 'og kun ba
NK041(di)030:692: thag gzengs pa ltar 'phros pas sa 'og sa steng
NK041(di)030:693: sa bla'i khams thams cad khyab /
NK041(di)030:694: bla tshe la bar du gcod pa'i steng gdon gza' dang rgyu skar /
NK041(di)030:696: bar gdon btsan dang rgyal po la sogs mdor na
NK041(di)030:697: bgegs gdon gyi rigs su gyur pas brkus pa dang
NK041(di)030:703: yon gyi bdag por bstims pas /
NK041(di)030:707: sngar bas kyang gzi byin dang ldan pas /
NK041(di)030:709: mi nor zas gsum la sogs pa rgyas shing brtan
NK041(di)030:710: par gyur par mos la spros bsdu'i dmigs pa yang
NK041(di)030:711: yang bya zhing sngags zur gsal dkyus su bkod pa
NK041(di)030:712: ni / a ha ri ni sa dz+hab dz+ha ba
NK041(di)030:713: rdzub rdzub b+ha dra slong slong n+rihkhuga dzahdzah brgya stong
NK041(di)030:714: khri 'bum sogs rtags dang sbyar te bazla'o //
NK041(di)030:715: skabs 'dir gter chen gsung la khams pa kun dga'
NK041(di)030:716: bstan 'dzin gyis zin bris mdzad pa las yi dam
NK041(di)030:717: gyi sngags sham du sngags 'di btags nas bzla dgos
NK041(di)030:718: par gsungs shing phal cher gyis phyag len tu mdzad
NK041(di)030:719: par snang ngo // de ltar thun drug gam bzhir bcad pa'i cho ga bzlas pa bcas byed /
NK041(di)030:720: dngos nyams rmi lam gyi ltas dang bstun nas skabs
NK041(di)030:721: su bla ma 'khyams pa'i gnas rnams nas mi ming
NK041(di)030:722: lo khams 'di zhes bya ba'i bla tshe 'khyams pa
NK041(di)030:723: sogs khug cig pa'i tshig skad gsang mthon pos 'bod
NK041(di)030:724: cing bstims pa'i mos pa brtan po byed par bshad
NK041(di)030:725: pa ltar / nang nub gung gnyis sogs su khang
NK041(di)030:726: steng bskor te phyogs kun tu thos nges pa'i skad
NK041(di)030:727: kyis 'og gi 'gugs tshig ltar 'bod pa dang /
NK041(di)030:728: yang che gnyan gyi rigs la thog steng nas mda'
NK041(di)030:729: dar g.yab cing skad dma' bar 'bod pa'i lag len
NK041(di)030:730: snang ba'ang byas na legs mod /
NK041(di)030:731: dkyus su thun 'jug so sor bden brdar dgug gzhug mdzad pa'i phyag len ltar na /
NK041(di)030:734: rig 'dzin rtsa brgyud kyi dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK041(di)030:735: dkon mchog rin po che rnam pa gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK041(di)030:736: yi dam rgyal ba zhi khro dpa' bo mkha' 'gro
NK041(di)030:737: chos skyong srung ma'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi
NK041(di)030:739: gsang sngags rigs sngags gzungs sngags snying po phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK041(di)030:740: chos nyid rnam par dag cing chos can rten 'brel bslu ba med pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK041(di)030:743: dge 'dun gyi kun dga' ra ba dang /
NK041(di)030:745: grong khyer chen po'i srang mdo /
NK041(di)030:747: lha srin gdug rtsub can gnas pa'i sa nas tshe
NK041(di)030:748: dang ldan pa ming rus lo khams so sor smos
NK041(di)030:749: pa'i bla tshe nyams pa dang /
NK041(di)030:756: byad ma lha srung gis bkug pa thams cad rang gnas su khug cig /
NK041(di)030:757: ces rol mo 'gugs sngags dang bcas pa lan gsum bya /
NK041(di)030:758: skabs mtshams su yon bdag dngos sam bla rten gang
NK041(di)030:759: rung gi mdun tu kha gtad de bla lug chu
NK041(di)030:761: dmod bor bas kha yon bdag gi bla rten phyogs
NK041(di)030:762: su gtad de bsdad na khug rtags yin pas mjug
NK041(di)030:764: phyir log tu bsdad na cho ga sngags bzlas sogs la 'bad cing bskyar la brtag go //
NK041(di)030:765: de ltar thun gsum sogs tshar grangs du byed la
NK041(di)030:766: re re bzhin glud mdos 'bru sna zan dum sogs
NK041(di)030:767: kyis kha gso / gser skyems snga ma phyi rol du mchod la gsar du bsham /
NK041(di)030:768: sngags drug phyag drug sngags rkyang pa tsam brjod la phyag rgya dang dmigs pas byin brlab /
NK041(di)030:769: spyan 'dren nas 'gugs pa yan chad la grangs bzung /
NK041(di)030:770: dgong mor chos srung gtor skyong chad brtan nas shis
NK041(di)030:771: brjod par lha gzhung gi rjes chog tshang bar bya'o
NK041(di)030:772: // de nas nyin gcig yin na tshar rjes ma /
NK041(di)030:773: zhag grangs byed na rdzogs pa'i skabs su 'gugs gzhug yan grub nas /
NK041(di)030:774: gsum pa mjug gi cho ga snang srid lha 'dre spyir bsngosa te gshegs su gsol la /
NK041(di)030:775: las gzhung gi mjug bsdu ba dang bcas pa ni /
NK041(di)030:776: thog mar yi dam gyi bskul yod na btang /
NK041(di)030:777: chos skyong gtor 'bul byas la glud kyi mar me sbar te /
NK041(di)030:779: snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre dang //
NK041(di)030:780: bkrag dang mdangs la dbang ba rnams //
NK041(di)030:781: rgyu sbyor yon gyi bdag po yis //
NK041(di)030:782: dka' ba btsal zhing dkon pa bsdus //
NK041(di)030:783: legs dgu bsags shing zhim dgu spungs //
NK041(di)030:784: bdag gis bsam pa rnam dag cing //
NK041(di)030:785: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs te //
NK041(di)030:786: snang srid lha 'dre dgyes byed pa'i //
NK041(di)030:787: 'dod yon drug ldan mchod gtor dang //
NK041(di)030:788: dbul ba'i glud chen 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)030:789: bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung la nyon //
NK041(di)030:790: chos nyid bden pa'i don la soms //
NK041(di)030:791: dbang gi rgyal po'i bka' ma bcag /
NK041(di)030:792: rig 'dzin rgyal po'i ngag la nyon //
NK041(di)030:793: rang gi lus la dpe longs la //
NK041(di)030:794: pha rol gzhan la gnod ma byed //
NK041(di)030:796: lung pa yi ni sum mdo na //
NK041(di)030:797: lam 'phrang de ni bzhi mdo na //
NK041(di)030:798: lha srin bskyod pa'i gnas shig mchis //
NK041(di)030:799: mdos glud dam pa 'di longs la //
NK041(di)030:801: skyod cig gshegs shig da gshegs shig /
NK041(di)030:802: rang rang so so'i gnas su gshegs //
NK041(di)030:803: zhes brjod la bla rten bla rkang sogs las gzhung gi gtor ma'i mdun du bsdu /
NK041(di)030:804: yas rnams phyogs skyel byed na ma nor bar snod bcur bsdu /
NK041(di)030:805: de min bsgrub bya'i 'dre lnga bdud gcod lta bu'i
NK041(di)030:806: phyogs gcig tu bskyal na phyi nas rim bzhin snod
NK041(di)030:808: thog mar dkar gtor gser skyems khyer /
NK041(di)030:809: de rjes yas rnams phyir spags /
NK041(di)030:810: de rgyab sa stegs yin na bsdus la bzhag /
NK041(di)030:811: de rgyab chad tho'i gtor zor bsham /
NK041(di)030:812: mdos stan gzhan yin na sprugs pa dang bstun /
NK041(di)030:814: de'ang spyi 'gro gang rung gis chog la /
NK041(di)030:815: 'don bya nges pa med pa'i rigs la phyogs 'di'i
NK041(di)030:816: phyag srol chags med rin po ches mdzad pa ltar
NK041(di)030:818: gser skyems zag pa med pa'i bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'dod yon gyi sprin phung 'phro bar gyur /
NK041(di)030:821: nga ni khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK041(di)030:822: thams cad nga yi bka' la nyon //
NK041(di)030:823: sngon mo 'bru yi snying khu ste //
NK041(di)030:824: rin chen dam pa gser bdar nas //
NK041(di)030:825: bla ma dkon mchog yi dam lha //
NK041(di)030:827: de ring gzu dang dpang po mdzod //
NK041(di)030:828: ma h+aa k+aa la lcam dral dang //
NK041(di)030:829: dpal mgon bdun cu 'khor dang bcas //
NK041(di)030:830: ma thogs tshur mchis skyems la byon //
NK041(di)030:831: rin chen gser skyems 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)030:832: bar chad rkyen rnams bzlog tu gsol //
NK041(di)030:833: gza' brgyad gdong mo rgyu skar tshogs //
NK041(di)030:834: dbyug gu drug cu mkha' 'gro bdun //
NK041(di)030:835: sa bdag rje blon bcu bdun sogs //
NK041(di)030:836: dus tshod tshes grangs bdag po rnams //
NK041(di)030:837: ma thogs tshur mchis skyems la byon //
NK041(di)030:838: rin chen gser skyems 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)030:839: ko long phrag dog ma mdzad cig /
NK041(di)030:840: sde brgyad yul lha gzhi yi bdag /
NK041(di)030:841: yul dang sa skor khang khyim 'dir //
NK041(di)030:842: gnyug mar gnas pa ma lus kun //
NK041(di)030:843: ma thogs tshur mchis skyems la byon //
NK041(di)030:844: rin chen gser skyems 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)030:845: ru nga phrag dog ma byed cig /
NK041(di)030:846: mtho mtho rnams kyi zhabs yar skum //
NK041(di)030:847: dma' dma' rnams kyi dbu chum zhig /
NK041(di)030:848: thad du 'dug pa sku bzur cig /
NK041(di)030:849: rin chen gser skyems 'di bzhes la //
NK041(di)030:850: mdos dang zor gyi lam phyes shog /
NK041(di)030:851: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK041(di)030:852: ces mdos btang phyogs su dkar gtor bcas phul /
NK041(di)030:853: las gzhung gi chad tho btang la mdos btegs /
NK041(di)030:854: phyogs bskyal skabs phyogs mtshams steng 'og bcu dang /
NK041(di)030:855: phyogs gcig la bsgrub bya'i lo lha min pa 'os pa'i phyogs su bskyal gzhug /
NK041(di)030:857: gzhan yang bzlog cing bsgyur ba ni //
NK041(di)030:860: mdos zor sha khrag gtor ma 'dis //
NK041(di)030:861: zhes pa lta bu'i zlog byang spyi rgyug gang shes
NK041(di)030:862: brjod la chad tho'i gtor ma mdos rjes zor du
NK041(di)030:863: 'phen / spro na lok+t+ri dang seng gdong ma lta bu'i zlog pa thal rdeb bcas pa'ang bya /
NK041(di)030:864: rjes su brtan ma bskyang zhing bro brdung /
NK041(di)030:865: bsgrub bya la srung 'khor brtan po bsgom /
NK041(di)030:867: dngos grub len pa sogs las gzhung gi mjug chog
NK041(di)030:868: dkyus ltar byed cing bkra shis pa'i tshigs su bcad
NK041(di)030:869: pa dang bstun me tog sil ma phyogs kun tu
NK041(di)030:870: 'thor / tshe sgrub dang sbrel skabs rgyas par spro
NK041(di)030:871: na bsgrub bya gos rgyan bzang po dang stan dkar
NK041(di)030:872: g.yung drung gi ri mo can la bzhag ste tshe
NK041(di)030:875: 'khor lo yod na dang bla g.yu mgul du gdags /
NK041(di)030:876: zhal bsro'i tshul du tshogs 'khor gyi dga' ston la longs spyad du gzhug /
NK041(di)030:877: bla rkang dang bla nas rnams kyang ltas brtags pa zin nas bsgrub bya rang nyid kyis bza' /
NK041(di)030:878: bla rtags bla lug rnams byi ba sogs kyi gnod pa mi 'byung ba'i sar spa'o //
NK041(di)030:880: rtsa ba'i gsum pa rtags la dpyad pa la'ang /
NK041(di)030:881: dang po bla rkang la brtag pa /
NK041(di)030:882: gnyis pa nas la brtag pa /
NK041(di)030:883: gsum pa rmi lam la brtag pa ste gsum las /
NK041(di)030:885: bla rkang gi rgya bshig la legs par blta /
NK041(di)030:886: de yang phyi rus pa la brtag pa /
NK041(di)030:887: nang chu ser la brtag pa /
NK041(di)030:888: gsang ba dri la brtag pa ste gsum las /
NK041(di)030:894: yang la chung ba rnams ngan pa yin /
NK041(di)030:895: khyad par rkang lag gog bkas ser ka spu ris byung na ngan zhing /
NK041(di)030:896: ma byung na mchog tu bzang ngo //
NK041(di)030:897: gnyis pa nang chu ser la brtag pa ni /
NK041(di)030:898: chu ser gyi sbu gu stod du 'dug na bzang /
NK041(di)030:901: de la'ang zhib par mdog la brtag ste /
NK041(di)030:905: gsum pa gsang ba dri la brtag pa ni /
NK041(di)030:908: sman dri ste dri bzang byung na bzang ba yin /
NK041(di)030:911: rul dri ste dri ngan byung na ngan pa yin pas legs par dpyad /
NK041(di)030:912: gnyis pa nas rdog la brtag pa ni /
NK041(di)030:913: bla rkang gi khrod du bcug pa'i nas sngar bas mang du yod na bzang /
NK041(di)030:915: rang sar bsdad na 'bring yin pas skyon med /
NK041(di)030:919: gsum pa rmi lam brtag pa ni /
NK041(di)030:920: rang ngam yon gyi bdag po'i rmi lam du g.yu btags pa dang /
NK041(di)030:924: g.yung drung gi ri mo la sogs rmis na mchog tu bzang ngo //
NK041(di)030:925: de ltar thams cad bzang rtags su byung na mchog tu legs /
NK041(di)030:926: phyed tsam bzang la phyed tsam ngan na 'bring ste ma bskyar rung chog /
NK041(di)030:927: ngan pa mang na slar lan gsum du bskyar bar bya'o //
NK041(di)030:928: rtags legs na bla g.yu lus la 'bral med gdags shing /
NK041(di)030:929: bla rkang gi sha phyi 'khyar med pa bsgrub byas
NK041(di)030:930: bza' ba dang bstun phye mar gyis zhal bsro bar
NK041(di)030:931: bya'o // zhes slob dpon chen po sgeg pa'i rdo
NK041(di)030:932: rjes mdzad pa'i bla bslu bcu gsum gyi yig rnying
NK041(di)030:933: gzhir bzhag gi steng phyag bzhes zab mos zur brgyan
NK041(di)030:934: te 'grigs chags go bder bkod pas 'gro la phan
NK041(di)030:935: bya'o // par gyur cig / chos ldan 'tsho ba lhun chags ri dbang bzhin //
NK041(di)030:936: bla tshe srog gi rdo rje'i ka ba nyid //
NK041(di)030:937: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i btsas su 'di gyur te //
NK041(di)030:938: 'brel tshad 'chi bdag 'jigs las grol gyur cig /
NK041(di)030:939: ces mchog dman kun la lan tsh+wa'i zas bzhin brim
NK041(di)030:940: yang gzhung mthun lag len byed pa dkon par mthong
NK041(di)030:941: bas / rtsa gzhung nyid lung rgyun bar ma chad
NK041(di)030:942: par snang bas sor bzhag thog gzhan la phan pa'i
NK041(di)030:943: bsam pas gsal byed kyis brgyan te pad+ma gar dbang
NK041(di)030:944: blo gros mtha' yas pa'i sdes rdzong shod bde gshegs
